{"tid":1875532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國郵政署回覆《蘋果》：未停止寄送中港澳郵件，但不能保證可準時送件到目的地","createTime":"2020-02-11T23:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T01:41:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5baab3bee5117d4b2a76e8bfc6ef8416df8a3a","tid":1875532,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T23:49:38.000Z","msg":"網購口罩既人可放心， 但要等<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200212/ZPIALVJ3RONIJN5AOSWDAAT23U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200212%2FZPIALVJ3RONIJN5AOSWDAAT23U%2F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2Bdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=686ff89b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200212%2FZPIALVJ3RONIJN5AOSWDAAT23U%2F&h=6a5b822b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200212/ZPIALVJ3RONIJN5AOSWDAAT23U/</a><br />\n<br />\n美聯社今日早上報道，美國郵政署已停止接收送件到香港、中國或澳門的服務。但美國郵政署（USPS）回覆《蘋果》查詢澄清，有關報導為錯誤訊息。美國郵政署仍然接收寄到香港、中國或澳門的郵件。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於大量航班取消、機位不足及入境困難等原因，由美國時間2月10日起暫停快遞承諾，當局不能夠確保寄往香港或中國的「國際空郵快遞」可以準時送到目的地（temporarily suspended the guarantee on Priority Mail Express International destined for China and Hong Kong）。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國郵政署已停止由第三國寄出，經美國郵政國際服務中心，送到香港、中國或澳門的轉運服務（transit mail）。"},{"pid":"a57c951d5e6477f8eac0423d656a4f4473bace8d","tid":1875532,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64342e782cde6a0b7ea672039b824073f0bba84c","tid":1875532,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:33:12.000Z","msg":"d人on99亂鳩咁forward"},{"pid":"2bf51e3834aa50a63d154783d6f94668eaa04c87","tid":1875532,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7i8ALuW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7i8ALuW.png&h=0bec9fba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n點解d人會見到呢句野就會覺得唔收件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}